SOUNDSNIP

THE AUDIO TIME MACHINE.

Whenever there was a
remarkable moment:
Tap once and SoundSnip captures
the last minute of sound
on your phone.

SoundSnip reinvents audio recording

Always ready

SoundSnip can capture the last moment at any given time of the day. This enables you to capture all of your life’s outstanding moments instantly.

Saves only what matters

Unlike classical recorders: SoundSnip only captures the last minute when you want it. Instead of hour long recordings you get digestible pieces of your best moments.

Super battery efficient

We optimized SoundSnip over and over again to consume as less battery as possible. You can keep it running an entire day in the background without ever recharging your phone.

HOW IT WORKS

hear

SoundSnip runs in the background constantly recording a 60 second audio loop

tap

tap your smartphone or smartwatch to capture the last minute of audio

manage & share

use SoundSnip to tag and manage your ‘Snips’ privately and share them with whoever you want

SoundSnip runs on your android wear smartwatch too

  • Stay fully in the moment without getting distracted.
  • One tap on your smartwatch and the last minute gets synced to your smartphone.
